Package stars.entity

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    NotificationInterface
    This interface provides a layer of abstraction for Student to call the sendNotification method without having to know whether an EmailSerivce is being used or an SMSService, etc is being used so that the Notification mechanism is extensible and the Notification methods are interchageable.
    Selectable
    This interface allows objects that implement it to display their information
  • Class Summary

    Course
    Course handles the data that pertains to a Course
    Database
    Contains the Information regarding the Students and Courses
    EmailService
    Handles the notification to be sent to the Student once the Student is moved from the waitlist to the confirmed list of the Index
    Index
    In charge of handling the data that belongs to an Index
    Student
    In charge of handling student data
    StudentRegisteredCourses
    In charge of the handling the Courses registered by the Student
    Timing
    Stores a timeslot that corresponds to Tutorial, Lecture or Lab session
  • Enum Summary
    Enum Description
    Timing.Day
    Provides the group of constants for the Day of that Timing (MON, TUE, WED, THU, FRI)
    Timing.Type
    Provides the group of constants for the Type of Session (Tutorial, Lab, Lecture) that the Timing corresponds to
